            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1678376282376-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained cannellini beans </strong>to the pot with your <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong>, <strong>Henderson’s Relish</strong>,<strong> vegetable</strong> <strong>stock </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 6-8 min or until thickened – these are your<strong> beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
