    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dust a work surface with a small handful of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry </strong>and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>puff pastry</strong> into 1 rectangle per person and add to a <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong>-lined tray (or two!)</p>",
